trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.CodeDom.CodeExpression" /> objects.
Provides a simple collection object that can represent a set of Code Document Object Model (CodeDOM) expression objects.
trans-unit.target: 提供可代表一組程式碼文件物件模型 (CodeDOM) 的運算式物件的簡單集合物件。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeExpressionCollection> class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeExpression> objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeExpressionCollection> 類別提供可用來儲存一組 <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeExpression> 物件的簡單集合物件。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the use of the <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeExpressionCollection> class methods.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何使用<xref:System.CodeDom.CodeExpressionCollection>類別方法。

trans-unit.source: The example creates a new instance of the class and uses the methods to add statements to the collection, return their index, and add or remove attributes at a specific index point.
trans-unit.target: 範例會建立類別的新執行個體，並使用方法來陳述式加入至集合，傳回其索引，新增或移除特定索引處的屬性。
